Title : 2014 Western Canada Cup
Text : The '''2014 [[Western Canada Cup]]''' was played at [[Credit Union Place]] in [[Dauphin, Manitoba]] from April 26 to May 4, 2014.<ref>[http://www.portageonline.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=29626%3Adauphin-picked-to-host-2014-western-canada-cup&Itemid=525 Dauphin picked to host 2014 Western Canada Cup]</ref> The [[Yorkton Terriers]] and host [[Dauphin Kings]] finished first and second, respectively, to each earn a berth in the [[2014 Royal Bank Cup]].<ref>[http://www.yorktonthisweek.com/article/20140507/YORKTON0201/140509887/-1/yorkton0201/taking-a-look-at-the-2014-royal-bank-cup-teams&template=JQMArticle Taking a look at the 2014 Royal Bank Cup teams]</ref>

